nisbet.andrew.notecrawler
Class Preprocessor

java.lang.Object
  nisbet.andrew.notecrawler.Preprocessor

public class Preprocessor
extends java.lang.Object

A convenience class for opening the note file. You may place a AUTHOR:author name on a single line and or a TITLE: on a single line. You may retrieve these values with their associated methods getAuthor(), or getTitle();

Author:
anisbet
